<text><body>
<cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">寺宇</cb:mulu><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">龍興寺天王殿</cb:mulu>
<milestone unit="juan" n="3"/>
<pb ed="GA" xml:id="GA029.0028.0077a" n="0077a"/>
<lb ed="GA" n="0077a01"/><cb:mulu type="卷" n="3"></cb:mulu><cb:juan fun="open" n="3"><cb:jhead>龍興祥符戒壇寺志卷三</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb ed="GA" n="0077a02"/><byline cb:type="collector">仁和張大昌輯</byline>
<lb ed="GA" n="0077a03"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">古蹟</cb:mulu><head>古蹟</head>
<lb ed="GA" n="0077a04"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">法華塔</cb:mulu><head>法華塔</head>
<lb ed="GA" n="0077a05"/><p xml:id="pGA029p0077a0501" style="margin-left:1em">咸湻臨安志舊志有法華塔端拱元年僧文定建
<lb ed="GA" n="0077a06"/>咸平二年賜名輿地紀勝法華塔在杭州府城祥
<lb ed="GA" n="0077a07"/>符寺建塔以七寶打碎<reg>為</reg>末和漆成之鍼血書法
<lb ed="GA" n="0077a08"/>華經內外佛像萬餘皆七寶所成</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="GA" n="0077a09"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">天中塔</cb:mulu><head>天中塔</head>
<lb ed="GA" n="0077a10"/><p xml:id="pGA029p0077a1001" style="margin-left:1em">國一禪師傳貞元九年德宗諡號曰貞元大覺禪
<pb ed="GA" xml:id="GA029.0028.0078a" n="0078a"/>
<lb ed="GA" n="0078a01"/>師塔曰天中</p><p xml:id="pGA029p0078a0106" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline">祥符古志略大覺禪師塔唐貞元
<lb ed="GA" n="0078a02"/>年建今民家葉姓屋下</p><p xml:id="pGA029p0078a0210" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline">玉几山房聽雨錄順治
<lb ed="GA" n="0078a03"/>初長白佟公國器重修</p><p xml:id="pGA029p0078a0310" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline">張尚美瞻禮尊勝幢探
<lb ed="GA" n="0078a04"/>索徑山國一禪師<reg>真</reg>身塔緣起唐國一禪師<reg>為</reg>徑
<lb ed="GA" n="0078a05"/>山開山元祖考徑山志師末順刺史之請居州之
<lb ed="GA" n="0078a06"/>龍興寺及將示滅於龍興先期三日告<reg>眾</reg>曰當葬
<lb ed="GA" n="0078a07"/>吾於南庭隙地勿封勿樹恐妨僧徒菜地等語德
<lb ed="GA" n="0078a08"/>宗追諡貞元大覺禪師賜其塔曰天中至天復中
<lb ed="GA" n="0078a09"/>錢氏裂土許再思兵亂發塔見二缸合藏肉身如
<lb ed="GA" n="0078a10"/>生髮長覆面士卒悚拜而去吳越王以厚禮重葬
<pb ed="GA" xml:id="GA029.0028.0079a" n="0079a"/>
<lb ed="GA" n="0079a01"/>於舊塔因是人始知師全身不散之塔的在於龍
<lb ed="GA" n="0079a02"/>興矣</p><p xml:id="pGA029p0079a0203" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline">今塔覆於佛殿西首累石<reg>為</reg>臺塑像於上</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="GA" n="0079a03"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">鐵塔</cb:mulu><head>鐵塔</head>
<lb ed="GA" n="0079a04"/><p xml:id="pGA029p0079a0401" style="margin-left:1em">武林梵志戒壇院在祥符橋內有鐵塔基</p><p xml:id="pGA029p0079a0417" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline">咸湻
<lb ed="GA" n="0079a05"/>臨安志大鐵塔一在軍器所作院</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="GA" n="0079a06"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">大青石塔</cb:mulu><head>大青石塔</head>
<lb ed="GA" n="0079a07"/><p xml:id="pGA029p0079a0701" style="margin-left:1em">咸湻臨安志大青石塔二在軍器所作院</p><p xml:id="pGA029p0079a0717" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline">祥符
<lb ed="GA" n="0079a08"/>古志略青石塔在軍器所今廢</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="GA" n="0079a09"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">小石塔</cb:mulu><head>小石塔</head>
<lb ed="GA" n="0079a10"/><p xml:id="pGA029p0079a1001" style="margin-left:1em">咸湻臨安志小石塔二在寺門及黃六家</p><p xml:id="pGA029p0079a1017" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline">祥符
<pb ed="GA" xml:id="GA029.0028.0080a" n="0080a"/>
<lb ed="GA" n="0080a01"/>古志略一見在寺前民家</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="GA" n="0080a02"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">尊勝陀羅尼經石幢</cb:mulu><head>尊勝陀羅尼經石幢</head>
<lb ed="GA" n="0080a03"/><p xml:id="pGA029p0080a0301" style="margin-left:1em">祥符古志略幢二座一在柴房下一在俞屋下崇
<lb ed="GA" n="0080a04"/>禎丙子放光震地涌出<reg>眾</reg>善贖出</p>
<lb ed="GA" n="0080a05"/><p xml:id="pGA029p0080a0501" style="margin-left:2em">按今僅存一座詳下金石</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="GA" n="0080a06"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">慈雲普會寶塔石基</cb:mulu><head>慈雲普會寶塔石基</head>
<lb ed="GA" n="0080a07"/><p xml:id="pGA029p0080a0701" style="margin-left:1em">舊在慈雲禪院亂後院燬此石與甲乙流傳據帖
<lb ed="GA" n="0080a08"/>碑俱棄瓦礫中因移此石基供寺中方擬更移據
<lb ed="GA" n="0080a09"/>帖碑而已<reg>為</reg>收廢石者取去毀之莫可復究詳下
<lb ed="GA" n="0080a10"/>金石</p></cb:div>
<pb ed="GA" xml:id="GA029.0028.0081a" n="0081a"/>
<lb ed="GA" n="0081a01"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">觀音三昧井</cb:mulu><head>觀音三昧井</head>
<lb ed="GA" n="0081a02"/><p xml:id="pGA029p0081a0201" style="margin-left:1em">祥符古志略觀音三昧井在貓兒庵基</p><p xml:id="pGA029p0081a0216" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline">硯林詩
<lb ed="GA" n="0081a03"/>集石幢詩注觀音三昧井去經幢不數武塼甃參
<lb ed="GA" n="0081a04"/>差石闌已失又云三昧井只存窪水</p><p xml:id="pGA029p0081a0415" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline">今在佛殿
<lb ed="GA" n="0081a05"/>前重加浚治構石闌高二尺許足供寺中汲爨</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="GA" n="0081a06"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">錢王井</cb:mulu><head>錢王井</head>
<lb ed="GA" n="0081a07"/><p xml:id="pGA029p0081a0701" style="margin-left:1em">夢粱錄祥符寺中向吳越王于寺內開井九百九
<lb ed="GA" n="0081a08"/>十九眼後改創軍器所陻塞僅存數井耳</p><p xml:id="pGA029p0081a0817" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline">黃溍
<lb ed="GA" n="0081a09"/>龍興祥符戒壇寺記有司驗得鐵塔一石塔二古
<lb ed="GA" n="0081a10"/>井九</p><p xml:id="pGA029p0081a1003" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline">成化杭州府志吳越王開凡九十九眼今
<pb ed="GA" xml:id="GA029.0028.0082a" n="0082a"/>
<lb ed="GA" n="0082a01"/>湮塞僅存數井</p><p xml:id="pGA029p0082a0107" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline">康熙仁和縣志吳越王開有九
<lb ed="GA" n="0082a02"/>十九眼今湮塞僅存三</p><p xml:id="pGA029p0082a0210" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline">祥符古志略吳越王所
<lb ed="GA" n="0082a03"/>鑿散在寺內及民家</p><p xml:id="pGA029p0082a0309" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline">有正味齋詞注錢武肅王
<lb ed="GA" n="0082a04"/>於寺鑿九十九眼今百井坊巷疑<reg>即</reg>其地</p><p xml:id="pGA029p0082a0417" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline">北隅
<lb ed="GA" n="0082a05"/>掌錄咸湻志山川十六祥符寺井吳越王開凡九
<lb ed="GA" n="0082a06"/>百九十眼後<reg>為</reg>軍器所陻塞今僅存數井寺觀二
<lb ed="GA" n="0082a07"/>錢王井九百九十眼今存者無幾並云九百九十
<lb ed="GA" n="0082a08"/>夢粱錄同而湻祐志則云有井九十九眼洪武杭
<lb ed="GA" n="0082a09"/>州府志<note place="inline">書今不傳見永樂大典</note>有錢王所鑿九十九眼井成
<lb ed="GA" n="0082a10"/>化志同按此係咸湻志誤而夢粱錄承之湻祐洪
<pb ed="GA" xml:id="GA029.0028.0083a" n="0083a"/>
<lb ed="GA" n="0083a01"/>武成化三志是也樓宣獻武林山詩吳越大築緇
<lb ed="GA" n="0083a02"/>黃廬<reg>為</reg>穿百井以壓之尤<reg>為</reg>顯證今寺後有百井
<lb ed="GA" n="0083a03"/>坊巷當從此得名十國春秋寶正六年浚中興寺
<lb ed="GA" n="0083a04"/>戒壇院井井九十九眼則九十九是眼數非井數
<lb ed="GA" n="0083a05"/>明矣</p>
<lb ed="GA" n="0083a06"/><p xml:id="pGA029p0083a0601" style="margin-left:2em">按黃氏此說以九百九十之數<reg>為</reg>誤文良塙樓
<lb ed="GA" n="0083a07"/>攻媿詩夢粱錄引之則吳自牧自<reg>為</reg>矛盾也謂
<lb ed="GA" n="0083a08"/>是眼數非井數此說殊失之一井謂之一眼自
<lb ed="GA" n="0083a09"/>是常語或於井上石甃分數眼者亦有之如所
<lb ed="GA" n="0083a10"/>謂雙眼井四眼井是也其實石甃下只一眼耳
<pb ed="GA" xml:id="GA029.0028.0084a" n="0084a"/>
<lb ed="GA" n="0084a01"/>若於一井甃上鑿眼九十九<reg>既</reg>乏此巨石而其
<lb ed="GA" n="0084a02"/>井亦幾成蓮蕩若是分數井共鑿眼九十九則
<lb ed="GA" n="0084a03"/>井亦自有定數矣安得謂非井數哉今亂後重
<lb ed="GA" n="0084a04"/>浚在龍興菜地旁者二在祥符者一康熙縣志
<lb ed="GA" n="0084a05"/>云僅存三井今與相合</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="GA" n="0084a06"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">放生池</cb:mulu><head>放生池</head>
<lb ed="GA" n="0084a07"/><p xml:id="pGA029p0084a0701" style="margin-left:1em">北隅掌錄沈氏放生池沈氏東銓第前之二大池
<lb ed="GA" n="0084a08"/>也池之左右復有五池蔡木龕丈云其西北百步
<lb ed="GA" n="0084a09"/><reg>即</reg>予之是一蘧廬每雨池水泛溢遂合<reg>眾</reg>池之水
<lb ed="GA" n="0084a10"/>歸入一澗穿蘧廬入斜橋</p><p xml:id="pGA029p0084a1011" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline">毛奇齡記崇禎七年
<pb ed="GA" xml:id="GA029.0028.0085a" n="0085a"/>
<lb ed="GA" n="0085a01"/>沈澤民先生捨其池<reg>為</reg>放生池沈八公者<note place="inline">名荀龍</note>先
<lb ed="GA" n="0085a02"/>生之季子也以十五緡錢質貴門其友各齎一緡
<lb ed="GA" n="0085a03"/>贖之康熙三十七年重標曰放生池</p><p xml:id="pGA029p0085a0315" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline">嚴元照記
<lb ed="GA" n="0085a04"/>南庵之旁有池廣百有三十步亦捨以放生今又
<lb ed="GA" n="0085a05"/>湮廢吾友何君元錫家與南庵鄰及與同人醵金
<lb ed="GA" n="0085a06"/>先復其三之一以漸復其餘</p>
<lb ed="GA" n="0085a07"/><p xml:id="pGA029p0085a0701" style="margin-left:2em">按今池在戒壇寺後劫後未廢兩記石皆使全
<lb ed="GA" n="0085a08"/>文錄存金石見後嚴記在嘉慶十七年</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="GA" n="0085a09"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">寶極觀十景</cb:mulu><head>寶極觀十景</head>
<lb ed="GA" n="0085a10"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">孤雲訪道</cb:mulu><head>孤雲訪道</head><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="4">鳳陽苗衷詩</cb:mulu><head>鳳陽苗衷詩</head><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgGA029p0085a1010" cb:place="inline" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:0em;"><l style="text-indent:1em">身騎金虎佩蒼精　遠向
<pb ed="GA" xml:id="GA029.0028.0086a" n="0086a"/>
<lb ed="GA" n="0086a01"/>蓬萊謁舊盟</l><l style="text-indent:1em">千樹紅桃百壺酒　與君漫飲話長生</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="GA" n="0086a02"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="4">錢塘秦邦福詩</cb:mulu><head>錢塘秦邦福詩</head><lg xml:id="lgGA029p0086a0207" cb:place="inline" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:0em;"><l style="text-indent:1em">一卷老子書　靜領無<reg>為</reg>趣</l><l style="text-indent:1em">抽簪
<lb ed="GA" n="0086a03"/>扣雲關　只恐雲攔住</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="4">仁和林則茂詩</cb:mulu><head>仁和林則茂詩</head><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgGA029p0086a0315" cb:place="inline" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:0em;"><l style="text-indent:1em">可道非常
<lb ed="GA" n="0086a04"/>道　一片孤雲孤</l><l style="text-indent:1em">欲訪不知處　妙與天地樞</l></lg></cb:div></cb:div>
<lb ed="GA" n="0086a05"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">赤腳談玄</cb:mulu><head>赤腳談玄</head><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="4">邱南賈愚詩</cb:mulu><head>邱南賈愚詩</head><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgGA029p0086a0510" cb:place="inline" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:0em;"><l style="text-indent:1em">嬾著雙鳧姓便揚　也曾
<lb ed="GA" n="0086a06"/>因此動明王</l><l style="text-indent:1em">從來不受人纏縛　嬴得芳名萬古香</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="GA" n="0086a07"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="4">秦邦福詩</cb:mulu><head>秦邦福詩</head><lg xml:id="lgGA029p0086a0705" cb:place="inline" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:0em;"><l style="text-indent:1em">汗腳一尺三　不屨亦不襪</l><l style="text-indent:1em">衝口寓元
<lb ed="GA" n="0086a08"/>機　泉流而風發</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="4">林則茂詩</cb:mulu><head>林則茂詩</head><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgGA029p0086a0811" cb:place="inline" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:0em;"><l style="text-indent:1em">拖泥而帶水　腳重八
<lb ed="GA" n="0086a09"/>十斤</l><l style="text-indent:1em"><reg>真</reg>玄之又玄　實聞所未聞</l></lg></cb:div></cb:div>
<lb ed="GA" n="0086a10"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">蒼松雪鶴</cb:mulu><head>蒼松雪鶴</head><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="4">苗衷詩</cb:mulu><head>苗衷詩</head><lg xml:id="lgGA029p0086a1008" cb:place="inline" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:0em;"><l style="text-indent:1em">別卻緱山歲月長　琳宮樹色
<pb ed="GA" xml:id="GA029.0028.0087a" n="0087a"/>
<lb ed="GA" n="0087a01"/>更蒼蒼</l><l style="text-indent:1em">曉依樹葉煙籠玉　夜啄空庭月影霜</l><l style="text-indent:1em">引呪
<lb ed="GA" n="0087a02"/>每思銀甕水　聽經還履石壇香</l><l style="text-indent:1em">天風吹醒烟霞夢
<lb ed="GA" n="0087a03"/>　飛伴山遊覽八荒</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="4">秦邦福詩</cb:mulu><head>秦邦福詩</head><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgGA029p0087a0312" cb:place="inline" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:0em;"><l style="text-indent:1em">松髯蒼何疏　鶴髮
<lb ed="GA" n="0087a04"/>白且潔</l><l style="text-indent:1em">道人術長生　髯修髮如漆</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="4">林則茂詩</cb:mulu><head>林則茂詩</head><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgGA029p0087a0418" cb:place="inline" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:0em;"><l style="text-indent:1em">鶴
<lb ed="GA" n="0087a05"/>壽不知紀　雲情無此閒</l><l style="text-indent:1em">道人默爾息　靜日閉松關</l></lg></cb:div></cb:div>
<lb ed="GA" n="0087a06"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">玉沼金鱗</cb:mulu><head>玉沼金鱗</head><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="4">賈愚詩</cb:mulu><head>賈愚詩</head><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgGA029p0087a0608" cb:place="inline" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:0em;"><l style="text-indent:1em">一泓寒玉浸芙蓉　隔斷桃花
<lb ed="GA" n="0087a07"/>浪幾重</l><l style="text-indent:1em">釣餌不來香跡隱　此心無復望成龍</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="4">秦</cb:mulu><head>秦</head>
<lb ed="GA" n="0087a08"/>邦福詩<lg xml:id="lgGA029p0087a0804" cb:place="inline" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:0em;"><l style="text-indent:1em">石闌環方池　波影浮碧玉</l><l style="text-indent:1em">物理悟悠然　鱗
<lb ed="GA" n="0087a09"/>鱗三十六</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="4">林則茂詩</cb:mulu><head>林則茂詩</head><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgGA029p0087a0909" cb:place="inline" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:0em;"><l style="text-indent:1em">方流白於玉　沼上生遐心</l>
<lb ed="GA" n="0087a10"/><l style="text-indent:1em">莫謂金鱗小　能作三日霖</l></lg></cb:div></cb:div>
<pb ed="GA" xml:id="GA029.0028.0088a" n="0088a"/>
<lb ed="GA" n="0088a01"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">祖庭秋月</cb:mulu><head>祖庭秋月</head><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="4">苗衷詩</cb:mulu><head>苗衷詩</head><lg xml:id="lgGA029p0088a0108" cb:place="inline" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:0em;"><l style="text-indent:1em">虛亭幽敞夜漫漫　璧月流輝
<lb ed="GA" n="0088a02"/>照石壇</l><l style="text-indent:1em">影浸羽衣銀兔溼　光浮玉宇露華寒</l><l style="text-indent:1em">鉤簾
<lb ed="GA" n="0088a03"/>屢入杯中吸　掬水還從掌上乾</l><l style="text-indent:1em">幾度晚天風細細
<lb ed="GA" n="0088a04"/>　置身疑在五雲端</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="4">秦邦福詩</cb:mulu><head>秦邦福詩</head><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgGA029p0088a0412" cb:place="inline" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:0em;"><l style="text-indent:1em">圓靈證道心　涼爽
<lb ed="GA" n="0088a05"/>沁仙骨</l><l style="text-indent:1em">何煩申法師　御風游月窟</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="4">林則茂詩</cb:mulu><head>林則茂詩</head><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgGA029p0088a0518" cb:place="inline" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:0em;"><l style="text-indent:1em">近
<lb ed="GA" n="0088a06"/>祖張無<reg>為</reg>　遠祖張道陵</l><l style="text-indent:1em">月不分今古　空庭秋氣澄</l></lg></cb:div></cb:div>
<lb ed="GA" n="0088a07"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">仙閣朝霞</cb:mulu><head>仙閣朝霞</head><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="4">苗衷詩</cb:mulu><head>苗衷詩</head><lg xml:id="lgGA029p0088a0708" cb:place="inline" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:0em;"><l style="text-indent:1em">仙閣平明啟曙扉　九天霞彩
<lb ed="GA" n="0088a08"/>遠稀微</l><l style="text-indent:1em">千章捧日花間見　五色文成鳥外飛</l><l style="text-indent:1em">爛漫
<lb ed="GA" n="0088a09"/>繡紋浮錦障　鬱蔥佳氣晃朝衣</l><l style="text-indent:1em">道人已得長生術
<lb ed="GA" n="0088a10"/>　食盡精華養素機</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="4">秦邦福詩</cb:mulu><head>秦邦福詩</head><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgGA029p0088a1012" cb:place="inline" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:0em;"><l style="text-indent:1em">霞帔加星冠　曾膺
<pb ed="GA" xml:id="GA029.0028.0089a" n="0089a"/>
<lb ed="GA" n="0089a01"/>紫泥召</l><l style="text-indent:1em">紅牆紺宇間　榮光先照耀</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="4">林則茂詩</cb:mulu><head>林則茂詩</head><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgGA029p0089a0118" cb:place="inline" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:0em;"><l style="text-indent:1em">丹
<lb ed="GA" n="0089a02"/>光騰五色　豔豔鬬朝霞</l><l style="text-indent:1em">往來高閣上　仙子多於麻</l></lg></cb:div></cb:div>
<lb ed="GA" n="0089a03"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">觀橋春水</cb:mulu><head>觀橋春水</head><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="4">賈愚詩</cb:mulu><head>賈愚詩</head><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgGA029p0089a0308" cb:place="inline" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:0em;"><l style="text-indent:1em">門前流水綠迢迢　春抹鵞黃
<lb ed="GA" n="0089a04"/>上柳條</l><l style="text-indent:1em">半夜雨聲渾似洗　一篙新漲欲平橋</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="4">秦</cb:mulu><head>秦</head>
<lb ed="GA" n="0089a05"/>邦福詩<lg xml:id="lgGA029p0089a0504" cb:place="inline" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:0em;"><l style="text-indent:1em">長虹吸春水　門前緣無垢</l><l style="text-indent:1em">倦眼讀南華　潄
<lb ed="GA" n="0089a06"/>齒禮北斗</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="4">林則茂詩</cb:mulu><head>林則茂詩</head><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgGA029p0089a0609" cb:place="inline" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:0em;"><l style="text-indent:1em">三尺橋下水　澈底無纖塵</l>
<lb ed="GA" n="0089a07"/><l style="text-indent:1em">流出<reg>真</reg>丹液　蓬蓬生遠春</l></lg></cb:div></cb:div>
<lb ed="GA" n="0089a08"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">環林夕照</cb:mulu><head>環林夕照</head><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="4">會稽陳贄詩</cb:mulu><head>會稽陳贄詩</head><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgGA029p0089a0810" cb:place="inline" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:0em;"><l style="text-indent:1em">瑤草琅玕翠滿林　洞天
<lb ed="GA" n="0089a09"/>開處快登臨</l><l style="text-indent:1em">道人相契談玄久　不覺虛簷墮夕陰</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="GA" n="0089a10"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="4">秦邦福詩</cb:mulu><head>秦邦福詩</head><lg xml:id="lgGA029p0089a1005" cb:place="inline" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:0em;"><l style="text-indent:1em">瑤草接琪花　春長不知老</l><l style="text-indent:1em">背手看西
<pb ed="GA" xml:id="GA029.0028.0090a" n="0090a"/>
<lb ed="GA" n="0090a01"/>山　夕陽無限好</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="4">林則茂詩</cb:mulu><head>林則茂詩</head><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgGA029p0090a0111" cb:place="inline" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:0em;"><l style="text-indent:1em">福地洞天府　叢林環
<lb ed="GA" n="0090a02"/>其中</l><l style="text-indent:1em">世上三千年　一度斜陽紅</l></lg></cb:div></cb:div>
<lb ed="GA" n="0090a03"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">石壇丹桂</cb:mulu><head>石壇丹桂</head><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="4">慈湖江山詩</cb:mulu><head>慈湖江山詩</head><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgGA029p0090a0310" cb:place="inline" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:0em;"><l style="text-indent:1em">瓊樹婆娑發露叢　託根
<lb ed="GA" n="0090a04"/>曾在廣寒宮</l><l style="text-indent:1em">天風吹下金千斛　人醉虛壇月影中</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="GA" n="0090a05"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="4">秦邦福詩</cb:mulu><head>秦邦福詩</head><lg xml:id="lgGA029p0090a0505" cb:place="inline" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:0em;"><l style="text-indent:1em">天香落瑤臺　仙風澹秋味</l><l style="text-indent:1em">所寶惟不
<lb ed="GA" n="0090a06"/>貪　卻識金銀氣</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="4">林則茂詩</cb:mulu><head>林則茂詩</head><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgGA029p0090a0611" cb:place="inline" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:0em;"><l style="text-indent:1em">仙壇石百級　其上<reg>真</reg>
<lb ed="GA" n="0090a07"/>靈過</l><l style="text-indent:1em">桂子落如雨　天香雲外多</l></lg></cb:div></cb:div>
<lb ed="GA" n="0090a08"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">玄圃緋桃</cb:mulu><head>玄圃緋桃</head><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="4">苗衷詩</cb:mulu><head>苗衷詩</head><lg xml:id="lgGA029p0090a0808" cb:place="inline" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:0em;"><l style="text-indent:1em">東風吹暖報春華　玄圃新開
<lb ed="GA" n="0090a09"/>滿樹花</l><l style="text-indent:1em">平漲錦雲迷鶴氅　亂飄紅雨點丹砂</l><l style="text-indent:1em">當年
<lb ed="GA" n="0090a10"/>緱嶺應同品　比地元都足並誇</l><l style="text-indent:1em">片片盡隨流水去
<pb ed="GA" xml:id="GA029.0028.0091a" n="0091a"/>
<lb ed="GA" n="0091a01"/>　行人疑是武陵家</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="4">秦邦福詩</cb:mulu><head>秦邦福詩</head><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgGA029p0091a0112" cb:place="inline" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:0em;"><l style="text-indent:1em">幾叢灼灼華　和露
<lb ed="GA" n="0091a02"/>分天上</l><l style="text-indent:1em">瞬息三千年　蟠桃作供養</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="4">林則茂詩</cb:mulu><head>林則茂詩</head><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgGA029p0091a0218" cb:place="inline" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:0em;"><l style="text-indent:1em">武
<lb ed="GA" n="0091a03"/>陵在塵境　<g ref="#CB33476"/>倩亦凡夫</l><l style="text-indent:1em">自笑非劉郎　重來無一株</l></lg></cb:div></cb:div></cb:div></cb:div>
